Package usermain

Class Doctor

java.lang.Object
usermain.User
usermain.Doctor
public class Doctor extends User
The Doctor class represents a doctor in the hospital management system. It provides functionalities to manage appointments, update patient records, set availability, and view schedules and upcoming appointments.
